The '''GX-15 "Starbolt" [[Concussion missile/Legends|concussion missile]]''' was designed by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] following the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]] and was in fact an armor-piercing warhead.

It had a pseudointelligent guidance system which was capable of identifying and locking onto targets by simple verbal commands alone. Once it reached its target, it directed a concussive energy charge which was capable of blasting straight through a garrison wall or disable and, on some occasions, outright destroy an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[All Terrain Armored Transport/Legends|AT-AT]] with a well placed shot.

